This App is an SMS sendting/recieving Sms App that basically performs all the functions that a Normal Sms App does other than deleting the messages.

Libraries used are -
1 . Only gson library other than all the other basic libraries is used .


Depencies of the App =
 1.compile 'com.google.code.gson:gson:2.6.2'
 2.compile 'com.android.support:appcompat-v7:23.4.0'
 3.compile 'com.android.support:design:23.4.0'
 4.compile 'com.android.support:support-v4:23.4.0'
 5.compile 'com.android.support:cardview-v7:23.4.0'